Class Mp3File

java.lang.Object
  Mp3File

public class Mp3File
extends java.lang.Object

A simple class that allows a user to access and change the pathname, author, album, title and date of an mp3 file. Mp3 files can also be played. Basically this class represents some information about an Mp3 file.
